[{"id":"9a4f7615cf8e4d418e267878b290109b","from":"Emad Hanna","from_email":"ehanna@nysgmail.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[{"name":"DKIESQ@aol.com","email":"DKIESQ@aol.com"}],"subject":"Reports and Pictures","date":"2008-06-06T20:48:33.000Z","formatted_date":"Jun 6, 2008","formatted_time":"8:48 PM","body":" \n\nJeffrey,\n\n \n\nI'm not sure if you have seen all the updates on LSJ so I am attaching\nwhat I have received for you review.\n\n \n\nThanks \n\nSubject: 6-6-08 \n\n\t\n <http://www.kodakgallery.com/images/invisible.gif> \n\nIf you can't see the pictures in this email, click here to see it in a\nweb browser:\nhttp://www.kodakgallery.com/I.jsp?c=k0utekm.3ikwryo2&x=0&y=c7b4b9&locale\nid=en_US \n\n <http://www.kodakgallery.com/images/invisible.gif> \n\n \n\n <http://www.kodakgallery.com/images/invisible.gif> \n\nEmad has shared photos with you.\n\n <http://www.kodakgallery.com/images/invisible.gif> \n\n<http://www.kodakgallery.com/I.jsp?c=k0utekm.3ikwryo2&x=0&y=c7b4b9&local\neid=en_US> \n\n \n<http://www.kodakgallery.com/I.jsp?c=k0utekm.3ikwryo2&x=0&y=c7b4b9&local\neid=en_US> \n\nClick to view my photos\n<http://www.kodakgallery.com/I.jsp?c=k0utekm.3ikwryo2&x=0&y=c7b4b9&local\neid=en_US> \n\n06-06-08\n\n(1 album) \n\n <http://www.kodakgallery.com/images/invisible.gif> \n\n <http://www.kodakgallery.com/images/invisible.gif> \nYou're invited to view my online photos at the Gallery. Enjoy! \n\n- Emad\n\n \n\nView photos\n<http://www.kodakgallery.com/I.jsp?c=k0utekm.3ikwryo2&x=0&y=c7b4b9&local\neid=en_US>  \n\n\t\n <http://www.kodakgallery.com/images/invisible.gif> \n\n <http://www.kodakgallery.com/images/invisible.gif> \n\n <http://www.kodakgallery.com/images/invisible.gif> \n\nDo more with these photos! \n\n Buy Kodak\nprints<http://www.kodakgallery.com/images/share/prints_96x96.jpg> \n\n Create a\ncollage<http://www.kodakgallery.com/images/share/collage_96x96.jpg> \n\n Create a mini photo\nbook<h